RDF Coder API

Other Packages
com.asemantics.rdfcoder This package contains the CommandLine access point and the High Level API interface ( RDFCoder ).

com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model This package defines the RDF Code Model and the query facilities.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model.java This package provides the model for the Java profile.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model.ontology This package defines a basic ontology validator.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.profile Contains utility classes to define RDFCoder profiles.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.repository This package defines utility classes to handle a file system repository able to store and organize the library data.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.sourceparse This package defines a set of parser interfaces and implementations plus auxiliary classes.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.storage This package defines a Code Model database.
